 the line flux, and the line profile,\nindicate that the broad-line emission component is physically distinct from the\nnarrow-line emission component, and more tightly related to the outburst event.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Dec 2010 21:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
